<HEADLINE>
OUTDOORS: BIRDHOUSE LANDLORDS CATER TO RENT-FREE TENANTS 
</HEADLINE>
   (Duplication warning: also sent with `L' code)  
 (bl)  
 By STEPHEN C. SAUTNER   
 c.1998 N.Y. Times News Service    
<TEXT>
