</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-HIROSHIMA-ROTBLAT-ABOMB-NYTSF </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
WHY I JOINED _ AND LEFT _ THE A-BOMB PROJECT 
</HEADLINE>
   &HT;     (To publish this ``separate buy'' article, it must be purchased
