   SPACE-CHIMPS _ WASHINGTON _ The Air Force announces the
recipients of its chimpanzee divestiture effort at a Department of
Defense briefing on Thursday. The divestiture provides for the
continued care of the Air Force chimps used in research related to
the space program. (Montgomery, Cox News Service).
</P>
<P>
   PFISTERIA _ WASHINGTON _ White House chief of staff Erskine
Bowles, EPA administrator Carol Browner and other federal and North
