<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    COMMENTARY: GOOD NEWS VS. BAD VIBES FROM CYBERSPACE
 &HT;    Moving in (k) commentary and (f) financial categories for
release Sunday, Aug. 9.
 &HT;    By ANDREW J. GLASS
