   IRAQ-U.N. (United Nations) _ The world closed ranks Thursday to
berate Iraq for ending cooperation with United Nations arms
inspectors, and then sat back to see what moves Baghdad may make
next. By Barbara Crossette. With IRAQ-U.S.
