<HEADER>
A1435 &Cx1f; tad-z
r k &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-JOURNAL-ISRAEL-$ADV08     08-06 0639
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-JOURNAL-ISRAEL-$ADV08-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    JOURNAL: AMID CINEMA SEARCHES, EXPLODED PINATAS, A FOREIGNER
FACES ISRAELI SECURITY
 &HT;    With photo of Kaplow placed in the International folder on the
Cox Server.
