chairman of the House Resources Committee, has sent a letter to the
Southwest regional office of the U.S. Forest Service seeking the
names of all federal employees who ``are members of'' or ``have any
contact with'' Arizona environmental groups. Environmentalists call
the letter part of a `'which hunt,'' likening it to McCarthy-era
searches for Ccommunists in the ranks of government. By STEVE
