<HEADLINE>
AUTO SAFETY: YOU'RE ON CANDID CAMERA. PAY UP. 
</HEADLINE>
  
 (ATTN: Md., N.Y., Calif.)  (Duplication warning: also filed in `f' category) 
(mk) 
